1 Write permission: Give the permission to write the "include" directory to the web server.
2 Installation process- Go to http://www.yourdomain.com/path/admin.php

3- Setup the newsletter

Newsletter Admin Area
- Go to http://www.yourdomain.com/path/admin.php
- Fill the field with your password (set in during the installation process)